{ changed code }
// ...existing code...
{ changed code }
// ...existing code...

Here is an example of how you should use format an edit to an existing Person class:
class Person {
	// ...existing code...
	age: number;
	// ...existing code...
	getAge() {
		return this.age;
	}
}

